RADIUM LIFE TECH said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 82.54% to NT$300,115,000 from NT$1,718,731,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2012           6/2011
Sales            300,115         1,718,731   
YOY%             -82.54%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,566,953        7,129,910   
YOY%             -78.02% 
=================================================================
 